flex
flex is the fast lexical analyzer generator

github: https://github.com/westes/flex
license: modified BSD
license url: https://github.com/westes/flex/blob/master/COPYING

Default version: 98018e3f58d79e082216d406866942841d4bdf8a

Building
flex is packaged with autoconf and builds without major problems. The only catch
is that autoreconf is required.
